 102:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****          In Slave mode, if HAL_I2S_DMAStop is used to stop the communication, an error
 103:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****          HAL_I2S_ERROR_BUSY_LINE_RX is raised as the master continue to transmit data.
 104:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****          In this case __HAL_I2S_FLUSH_RX_DR macro must be used to flush the remaining data
 105:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****          inside DR register and avoid using DeInit/Init process for the next transfer.
