 136:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****             (++) RxHalfCpltCallback    : I2S Rx Half Completed callback
 137:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****             (++) ErrorCallback         : I2S Error callback
 138:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****             (++) MspInitCallback       : I2S Msp Init callback
 139:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****             (++) MspDeInitCallback     : I2S Msp DeInit callback
 140:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****           This function takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle, the Callback ID
 141:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****           and a pointer to the user callback function.
