 249:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****         (++) Polarity
 250:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s.c ****         (++) Full duplex mode
